795
01:05:34,689 --> 01:05:37,761
Debo pensar en mis invitados.

796
01:05:43,209 --> 01:05:44,642
Debo decir que...

797
01:05:44,889 --> 01:05:46,720
...trabajan bien.

798
01:05:46,969 --> 01:05:49,722
