de Europa y América.

890
01:13:10,849 --> 01:13:11,998
Sr. Taylor...

891
01:13:12,249 --> 01:13:16,401
...me temo que debo retirarme.
Me siento cansado.

892
01:13:16,609 --> 01:13:18,600
No me extraña. Sin...

893
01:13:18,849 --> 01:13:21,807
